Welcome:
	- Tasky knows about projects, tasks, notes, and tags.
	- Use the Tasky activity bar for Home, Projects, Searches, and Tags.
	- Mark tasks done with Cmd/Ctrl+D (@done).
	- Delete this text when you are ready to start your own lists.
To Create Items:
These are the new instructions
	- New task: Cmd/Ctrl+Enter
	- New project: Cmd/Ctrl+Alt+Enter
	- Indent with Tab; outdent with Shift+Tab.
	- Tag With…: Cmd/Ctrl+Alt+T
Saved Searches:
	Due Soon @search(@due)
	Priority @search(@priority)
Inbox:
	- Write the report @due(2026-07-15) @priority(1)
	- Review pull request @today
	A plain note under Inbox.
Work:
	Active:
		- Nested project demo @priority(3)
		- Another nested task @priority(2)
	- Top-level work task
Archive:
	- Archive completed work with Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+A (moves @done under Archive:). @project(Welcome)
	- Ship extension @done(2026-07-13) @project(Inbox)
	- Old completed item @done
